items.name: MULTIPART
desc: Specifies to use \"multipart/form-data\" as submit encoding.
Usually used when the form contains a file upload element.

items.name: TEXT
desc: Usually used if the FormSubmitMethod attribute has the value POST and the content should be reviewed as full text.

items.name: URL
desc: When the button is clicked, a URL set for the button is opened.
Specifies to use \"application/x-www-form-urlencoded\" as submit encoding.
Usually used if the FormSubmitMethod attribute has the value POST.
